"According to the Chinese Provisions on the Scope of Necessary Personal Information for Common Types of Mobile Internet Applications, Mi Browser's basic features include <font color=#333e64>search, content browsing, downloading, and security features</font>. If you tap <font color=#333e64>\"Agree\"</font> below, this means you agree to our collection and processing of the personal information necessary for us to provide basic browser services.
